<holidayType guid="ea27f8ae-cab4-40d8-a303-9c5e12b6284e" id="27429" nodeName="Hotels Managed by Inghams" isDoc="" updated="2021-12-29T10:31:08.8530000Z" parentGUID="9e164d02-7242-4fd2-a479-d5af2cd75823" nodeTypeAlias="holidayType" templateAlias="HolidayType" sortOrder="0" published="false" isBlueprint="false">
  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13067875/hotels-managed-by-inghams.jpg" alt="Hotels Managed by Inghams" data-udi="umb://media/60734dd1d7b045d5ba69f87c825a6f3f" /></p>
<p><span class="geolocation-title">Don’t just travel with Inghams – stay with Inghams too! Join us in one of our exclusive Lakes &amp; Mountains properties in France or Italy. Our two exclusive hotels are run by a team of friendly and welcoming Inghams staff and enjoy stunning locations in the mountains.</span></p>
<p>Our hotels are perfect for walking and cycling enthusiasts, or simply relaxing as you enjoy the tranquil surroundings and the fresh mountain air. Each of our exclusive hotels are situated close to the lifts, quickly whisking you high up the mountains to the walking trails and dramatic views.</p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="page-title"><strong>Our Hotels</strong></span></p>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><span class="geolocation-title"><strong><img src="/media/13067697/hotels-managed-by-inghams-chamonix_sapiniere_summer-2019.jpg" alt="Hotel Sapiniere - Chamonix" data-udi="umb://media/bbb5f972842a4606ac46f4a25c52ee45" /></strong></span></p>
<p><span class="geolocation-title"><strong>The Hotel Sapinière</strong></span></p>
<p><span class="geolocation-title"><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf}" title="France">France</a></strong></span></p>
<p>An excellent value hotel managed by Inghams, the Hotel Sapinière provides a daily continental buffet breakfast and packed lunch, afternoon tea with cake and a 3-course, evening buffet menu for 6 days of your 7 night holiday, giving you the opportunity for 1 evening to explore Chamonix’s incredible restaurants.</p>
<p>The charming Hotel <span>Sapinière</span> occupies a quiet location in Chamonix with stunning views over the Savoy meadow to the snow-capped peak of Mont Blanc. We might be biased but we believe it’s the best view in Chamonix.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/98e5917964c04bbf9caa7f5e69e9874e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/98e5917964c04bbf9caa7f5e69e9874e}" title="Hotel Sapiniere"><strong>More on Hotel Sapinière &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><strong><span class="geolocation-title"><img src="/media/13067698/hotels-managed-by-inghams-lavilla_alpigher_summer-2019.jpg" alt="Hotel Al Pigher - La Villa" data-udi="umb://media/c455666b7f944cc3bfb52fe4169bbc68" /></span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span class="geolocation-title">The Hotel Al Pigher</span></strong></p>
<p><span class="geolocation-title"><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/90cb69cf75424d74aff05c67e69b8667" href="/{localLink:umb://document/90cb69cf75424d74aff05c67e69b8667}" title="La Villa">La Villa</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy</a></strong></span></p>
<p>Situated among stunning Dolomite scenery, the Hotel Al Pigher is perfectly located for exploring the pretty Italian village of La Villa. The sauna and relaxation area provide panoramic views, while the sun terrace and bar are ideal for resting weary feet after a long day hiking in the mountains.</p>
<p>The Hotel Al Pigher is great value, with continental buffet breakfasts, packed lunches and a 3-course set evening menu buffet available for 6 nights. Free wine is included with evening meals, as well free afternoon tea and coffee served 6 days a week.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/69707a0ade534738bf6448210c905f14" href="/{localLink:umb://document/69707a0ade534738bf6448210c905f14}" title="Hotel Al Pigher"><strong>More on Hotel Al Pigher &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
